            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "So indeed it looks like it is not possible to update origin's default branch during a `git fetch ...` done during `vim.pack.update()`. It needs an extra `git remote set-head origin --auto`.\n\nIt doesn't look to me as reasonable to add an extra `git ...` system call that 1) requires an internet connection; 2) will be run for every plugin on every `vim.pack.update()`; 3) will be useful *very*, *very* rarely.\n\nI'll take another look later, but I think adding a note in the documentation (about \"delete\" - \"reinstall\") somewhere is a reasonable compromise.",
